race.comment: FREESPOOL (6) started big odds in far stiffer grade latest when finishing 6th over 300m at this track. Was a winner the start prior in easier at Northam. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. ARCTIC CROP (2) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and two minors from eight tries. Scored by 2.25 lengths last time (17.49) in a Grade 6 over 300m at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. CHAROS GRAND (5) is worth forgiving last start after finishing sixth (17.43) from Box 8 at this track over 300m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to feature in the finish. SHINBONER SMOKEY (1) is a last start winner worth following up.
